    .card-body {
        color: white;
    }
    pre{
        font-size: large;
    }
</style>
<div class="row text-center pt-3">
    <div class="col-4 mx-auto">
        <a style="text-decoration: none; color:black" href="/reports/new">
        <div class="card bg-dark">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h1>Add Data</h1>
            </div>
        </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4 mx-auto">
        <a style="text-decoration: none; color:black" href="/reports/select">
        <div class="card bg-dark ">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h1>New Report</h1>
            </div>
        </a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4 mx-auto">
        <a style="text-decoration: none; color:black" href="/reports/list">
            <div class="card bg-dark">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h1>Reports</h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </a>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row mt-4 col-12 mx-auto">
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body" style="color: black;">
            <div class="accordion" id="accordionOne">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            <h1><strong style="font-size: large;">Add Data</strong></h1>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <pre>
                                The Add Data tab allows you to upload a <strong style="color: red;">.csv file</strong>
                                which will then be structured automatically.

                                The formatting of the file <strong style="color: red;">should always</strong> be as follows:
                                
                                         startDate,endDate|Name1,ID1
                                         timestamps separeted by commas
                                         timestamps separeted by commas|Name2,ID2
                                         
                                 <span style="color: salmon;">please keep in mind that the format for dates is: dd/mm/yy</span>
                            </pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            <h1><strong style="font-size: large;">New Report</strong></h1>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <pre>
                                The New Report tab allows you to generate and save a payroll 
                                report by selecting a start and an end date.
                                
                                The Report will include a general overview of the selected period
                                and also a detailed description of each employees billing period.
                            </pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                            <h1><strong style="font-size: large;">Reports</strong></h1>
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <pre>
                                The Reports tab allows you to visualize all saved reports.

                                you are also able to see more details by clicking the <i style="color: blue;" class="fa fa-eye"></i> icon.

                                or delete a report by clicking the <i class="fa fa-trash" style="color: red;"></i> icon.
                            </pre>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>